{"type":"answer","id":203155,"parentType":"question","parentId":20867,"uid":40727,"contents":"<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/VOAWeishi-20180801-ProfSunWenguang/4509142.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/VOAWeishi-20180801-ProfSunWenguang/4509142.html</a><br>\n<pre><br>\n美国之音电视直播 嘉宾被山东警方强行阻止<br>\n</pre><br>\n<br>\n还有葱油@<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/people/%E8%8D%A3%E8%AA%89%E9%9D%9E%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91\">荣誉非国民</a>提过<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/12528\">https://pincong.rocks/article/12528</a>&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n<pre><br>\n能，刘晓波拿诺贝尔奖那年，我和我妈打电话聊这事。一提刘晓波名字，三秒内必断，我特意实验了三次。<br>\n</pre><br>\n<br>\n人工监听应该有权力可以听到任何一同电话。<br>\n<br>\n同时，也很可能已经有语音识别文字。<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kUF229i.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kUF229i.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kUF229i.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n（但是应该只能针对普通话。所以，为什么要打压地方语言文化（方言））<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5eE5gVG.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5eE5gVG.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5eE5gVG.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n同时也提一下<br>\n——发展本土语言文化，大家多讲家乡话，以本土文化为荣耀！<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/8KD3f8L.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8KD3f8L.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/8KD3f8L.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n希望大家多点使用家乡的语言，传承自己的根。<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/blxWFbD.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/blxWFbD.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/blxWFbD.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n多元文化，也是自由的重要体现！","date":"2020-03-13","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}